# Golden test for the human CLI stderr format on code 3 (not_found).
# plans/PLAN.md § "stderr format (human CLI path)" specifies:
#
#   line 1: error: <message>
#   followed by indented `  key: value` lines (type + data fields)
#   exit code: Code  (3 for not_found)
#
# lakitu init so the garage (and the characters dir) exist, then ask for a
# character that was never registered. character.show's handler returns
# character_not_found (code 3) and the human CLI path routes it through
# internal/cli/errfmt.Emit.

lakitu init
! stderr .

! lakitu character show ghost
stderr '^error: character "ghost" not found'
stderr '^  type: character_not_found'
stderr '^  name: ghost'
! stdout .
